parent = Mock()
fname = p(self.testdir, 'test.conf')
def f():
    with open(fname, 'w') as f:
        f.write('{}\n')
parent._init_config_file.side_effect = f
parent.config_file = fname
parent.owmdir = self.testdir
cut = OWMConfig(parent)
cut.set('key', '1')
self.assertEqual(cut.get('key'), 1)
